  <p>See also <a href="../../assets/using/embed-code.md">Embedding the Video Viewer on a Web Page.</a></p> 
  <p>See also <a href="../../assets/using/linking-urls-to-yourwebapplication.md">Linking URLs to your Web Application.</a></p> 
  <p>To deliver optimized images for a responsive site:</p> 
  <ol> 
   <li><p>Navigate to the image you want supply responsive code for and in the drop-down menu, tap or click <strong>Renditions</strong>.</p> <img imageRotate="0" src="assets/chlimage_1-422.png" /></li> 
   <li><p>Select a responsive image preset. The <strong>URL</strong> and <strong>RESS</strong> buttons appear. </p> 
