     <p>The selected asset <em>and</em> the selected image preset or viewer preset must be published to make the <strong>URL</strong> or <strong>RESS</strong> buttons available.</p> 
     <p>(Note that Dynamic Media - Hybrid mode requires you to publish image presets; Dynamic Media - Scene7 mode automatically publishes image presets.</p> 
    </note></li> 
   <li><p>Tap or click <strong>RESS</strong>. The responsive code displays.</p> 
